title: Ep. - 362 - KATE CHASTAIN REVIEWS BRAVO SHOWS SEEKING SISTER WIVES REVIEW
description:
Kate Chastain from Below Deck answers a speed round of questions about Bravo shows including Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, Real Housewives of New Jersey, and Real Housewives of New York.

 

Kelly Senyei is a chef, TV and podcast host, cookbook author and founder of Just a Taste. Kelly reviews this season of Seeking Sister Wife on TLC.
